00083 #if defined(__gl_h_) || defined(__GL_H__) || defined(__X_GL_H)
00084 #error gl.h included before glew.h
00085 #endif
00086 #if defined(__glext_h_) || defined(__GLEXT_H_)
00087 #error glext.h included before glew.h
00088 #endif
00089 #if defined(__gl_ATI_h_)
00090 #error glATI.h included before glew.h
00091 #endif
00092 
00093 #define __gl_h_
00094 #define __GL_H__
00095 #define __X_GL_H
00096 #define __glext_h_
00097 #define __GLEXT_H_
00098 #define __gl_ATI_h_

00100 #if defined(_WIN32)
00101 
00102 /*
00103  * GLEW does not include <windows.h> to avoid name space pollution.
00104  * GL needs GLAPI and GLAPIENTRY, GLU needs APIENTRY, CALLBACK, and wchar_t
00105  * defined properly.
00106  */
00107 /* <windef.h> */
00108 #ifndef APIENTRY
00109 #define GLEW_APIENTRY_DEFINED
00110 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00111 #    define APIENTRY __stdcall
00112 #  elif (_MSC_VER >= 800) || defined(_STDCALL_SUPPORTED) || defined(__BORLANDC__)
00113 #    define APIENTRY __stdcall
00114 #  else
00115 #    define APIENTRY
00116 #  endif
00117 #endif
00118 #ifndef GLAPI
00119 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00120 #    define GLAPI extern
00121 #  endif
00122 #endif
00123 /* <winnt.h> */
00124 #ifndef CALLBACK
00125 #define GLEW_CALLBACK_DEFINED
00126 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00127 #    define CALLBACK __attribute__ ((__stdcall__))
00128 #  elif (defined(_M_MRX000) || defined(_M_IX86) || defined(_M_ALPHA) || defined(_M_PPC)) && !defined(MIDL_PASS)
00129 #    define CALLBACK __stdcall
00130 #  else
00131 #    define CALLBACK
00132 #  endif
00133 #endif
00134 /* <wingdi.h> and <winnt.h> */
00135 #ifndef WINGDIAPI
00136 #define GLEW_WINGDIAPI_DEFINED
00137 #define WINGDIAPI __declspec(dllimport)
00138 #endif
00139 /* <ctype.h> */
00140 #if (defined(_MSC_VER) || defined(__BORLANDC__)) && !defined(_WCHAR_T_DEFINED)
00141 typedef unsigned short wchar_t;
00142 #  define _WCHAR_T_DEFINED
00143 #endif
00144 /* <stddef.h> */
00145 #if !defined(_W64)
00146 #  if !defined(__midl) && (defined(_X86_) || defined(_M_IX86)) && defined(_MSC_VER) && _MSC_VER >= 1300
00147 #    define _W64 __w64
00148 #  else
00149 #    define _W64
00150 #  endif
00151 #endif
00152 #if !defined(_PTRDIFF_T_DEFINED) && !defined(_PTRDIFF_T_) && !defined(__MINGW64__)
00153 #  ifdef _WIN64
00154 typedef __int64 ptrdiff_t;
00155 #  else
00156 typedef _W64 int ptrdiff_t;
00157 #  endif
00158 #  define _PTRDIFF_T_DEFINED
00159 #  define _PTRDIFF_T_
00160 #endif
00161 
00162 #ifndef GLAPI
00163 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00164 #    define GLAPI extern
00165 #  else
00166 #    define GLAPI WINGDIAPI
00167 #  endif
00168 #endif
00169 
00170 #ifndef GLAPIENTRY
00171 #define GLAPIENTRY APIENTRY
00172 #endif
00173 
00174 /*
00175  * GLEW_STATIC is defined for static library.
00176  * GLEW_BUILD  is defined for building the DLL library.
00177  */
00178 
00179 #ifdef GLEW_STATIC
00180 #  define GLEWAPI extern
00181 #else
00182 #  ifdef GLEW_BUILD
00183 #    define GLEWAPI extern __declspec(dllexport)
00184 #  else
00185 #    define GLEWAPI extern __declspec(dllimport)
00186 #  endif
00187 #endif
00188 
00189 #else /* _UNIX */
00190 
00191 /*
00192  * Needed for ptrdiff_t in turn needed by VBO.  This is defined by ISO
00193  * C.  On my system, this amounts to _3 lines_ of included code, all of
00194  * them pretty much harmless.  If you know of a way of detecting 32 vs
00195  * 64 _targets_ at compile time you are free to replace this with
00196  * something that's portable.  For now, _this_ is the portable solution.
00197  * (mem, 2004-01-04)
00198  */
00199 
00200 #include <stddef.h>
00201 
00202 /* SGI MIPSPro doesn't like stdint.h in C++ mode          */
00203 /* ID: 3376260 Solaris 9 has inttypes.h, but not stdint.h */
00204 
00205 #if (defined(__sgi) || defined(__sun)) && !defined(__GNUC__)
00206 #include <inttypes.h>
00207 #else
00208 #include <stdint.h>
00209 #endif
00210 
00211 #define GLEW_APIENTRY_DEFINED
00212 #define APIENTRY
00213 
00214 /*
00215  * GLEW_STATIC is defined for static library.
00216  */
00217 
00218 #ifdef GLEW_STATIC
00219 #  define GLEWAPI extern
00220 #else
00221 #  if defined(__GNUC__) && __GNUC__>=4
00222 #   define GLEWAPI extern __attribute__ ((visibility("default")))
00223 #  elif defined(__SUNPRO_C) || defined(__SUNPRO_CC)
00224 #   define GLEWAPI extern __global
00225 #  else
00226 #   define GLEWAPI extern
00227 #  endif
00228 #endif

00234 #ifndef GLAPIENTRY

00238 #endif /* _WIN32 */
